    "en": {
      "title": "Five people arrested for Gampaha Murder",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lanka Police arrested five suspects for shooting dead a man at a salon in Gampaha on the 6th of August.",
        "According to Police, the suspects are residents of Pethiyagoda, Makevita, and Kotuguda.",
        "Police have also seized a revolver and the car used by the suspects to carry out the shooting."
      ],
